                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8853" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0478</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1176 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“技术”赋能“业务”：管理者胜任力助力云南移动乡村振兴平台的诞生与成长</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Technology” Enables “Business”: Managerial Competence Fuels the Birth and Growth of Yunnan Mobile&#39;s Rural Revitalization Platform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈爽英，卢国君</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国移动集团的产业研究院</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胜任力；数字化服务平台；乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Competence, Digital Services Platform, Rural Revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了中国移动集团云南有限公司（以下简称“云南公司”）省级乡村振兴平台的建设及发展过程中，中国移动集团的产业研究院（以下简称“产研院”）技术负责人胡梦青和云南公司业务负责人唐义明合作的故事。他们在初期沟通中一拍即合，胡梦青具有强大的技术专业能力，唐义明则非常了解市场需求。在平台建设初期，两人遭遇了“技术”视角与“业务”视角的冲突带来的领导责难，但通过沟通顺利消除了质疑。在后续合作中，双方形成了高效的协作，制定出规范的平台运营模式，并选择重点地区进行示范标杆打造。最终，在两人通力合作下，云南平台成为移动集团全国范围内的应用典范和标杆。总体来说，本案例中两位主人公在各个阶段展现出了不同的胜任力，双方通过良好沟通，形成高效合作，实现知识与经验的互补，最终使项目获得成功。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the cooperation between Hu Mengqing, the technical leader of China Mobile Group&#39;s Industrial Research Institute (‘IRI’), and Tang Yiming, the business leader of China Mobile Group Yunnan Company Limited (‘Yunnan Company’), from the construction to development of the Yunnan provincial-level Rural Revitalization Platform. They hit it off right away during the initial communication, Hu Mengqing has a strong IT expertise while Tang Yiming has a sophisticated knowledge of market needs. In the early stage of platform construction, they encountered the conflict between the ‘technical’ perspective and the ‘business’ perspective, which brought about their leader&#39;s reproach, but they eliminated the doubts successfully through communication. In the follow-up cooperation, they formed an efficient collaboration, developed a standardised platform operation model, and selected key areas to build up demonstration benchmark. In the end, with their full co-operation, this platform became a nationwide application demonstration benchmark for the China Mobile Group. Overall, the two protagonists in this case demonstrated different competencies at various stages, and their good communication formed a efficient collaboration, and complemented each other&#39;s knowledge and experience, which ultimately led to the success of the project.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《数智化人力资源管理》、《人力资源管理与开发》、《战略人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胜任力、数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
